## 项目中自定义扩展 Spring

### 场景 1：自定义注解 + 自动代理
```java
// 定义注解
@Target(ElementType.METHOD)
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
public @interface RateLimit {
    int value() default 100;
}

// 自定义 BeanPostProcessor
@Component
public class RateLimitBeanPostProcessor implements BeanPostProcessor {
    @Override
    public Object postProcessAfterInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) {
        // 扫描方法上的 @RateLimit
        for (Method method : bean.getClass().getMethods()) {
            if (method.isAnnotationPresent(RateLimit.class)) {
                // 创建代理
                return Proxy.newProxyInstance(
                    bean.getClass().getClassLoader(),
                    bean.getClass().getInterfaces(),
                    (proxy, m, args) -> {
                        if (m.isAnnotationPresent(RateLimit.class)) {
                            // 限流逻辑
                            if (!rateLimiter.tryAcquire()) {
                                throw new RateLimitException();
                            }
                        }
                        return m.invoke(bean, args);
                    }
                );
            }
        }
        return bean;
    }
}
```

### 场景 2：全局配置加密
```java
@Component
public class EncryptionBeanPostProcessor implements BeanPostProcessor {
    @Override
    public Object postProcessBeforeInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) {
    	// 对带 @Encrypted 注解的字段自动解密
        Field[] fields = bean.getClass().getDeclaredFields();
        for (Field field : fields) {
            if (field.isAnnotationPresent(Encrypted.class)) {
                field.setAccessible(true);
                String encrypted = (String) field.get(bean);
                field.set(bean, decrypt(encrypted)); // 自动解密
            }
        }
        return bean;
    }
}
```

### 场景 3：Spring 监听器扩展
```java
// 容器启动后执行
@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)
public void onReady() {
    // 初始化缓存、预热数据
}
```

